Initial Log:
Removing unecessary Logs. Note that it is not a diary entry. It's an Official Logging Platform for logging progress. It will contain important updates, observations and strategies.
Goal is to increase marks to 100%.

Current Strategy:<hr>
Order: M -> P -> C

Try to complete each subject in 1 hour or before (No exception for maths)

Delocalised Strict Time Management: min. 3 questions every 10 minutes

DQ strategy
<hr>

Maximum Allowed Time For DQ of 1 paper: 2 Hr

=> Maximum for 1 subject of 1 paper: 40min

Strategy Update
In match the following questions with 2 questions linked, Always before solving anything look at options of both the questions. If They Have a Common Option, then you need to only solve that (or sometimes even not solve anything)

Last Month Preparation Strategy
  • Complete GRPs for Revision
  • Complete Allen and Fiitjee Test Questions, which give all star batch materials

List of All Deceptive Tricks in Questions
A list of deceptive questions are maintained at Google Keep under email hemantkumartwo@gmail.com
